con = self.connect(init_command='SELECT "bar"; SELECT "baz"', client_flag=
    CLIENT.MULTI_STATEMENTS)
cur = con.cursor()
cur.execute('SELECT 1; SELECT 2;')
self.assertEqual([(1,)], list(cur))
r = cur.nextset()
self.assertTrue(r)
self.assertEqual([(2,)], list(cur))
self.assertIsNone(cur.nextset())
